{"tid":1503120,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［重要］前線義士請保護好背囊","createTime":"2019-08-24T23:08:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T02:42:33.000Z","uid":42852,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9b9840b10104237cdcbc44bbd24c71dc9cda9d35","tid":1503120,"uid":42852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T23:08:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6moHznu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6moHznu.png&h=95dfd2a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇返尋日擊退速龍嗰條片發現<br />\n雖然大家做法正確<br />\n但係發現有隻速龍臨退之前，都搶走咗個迪卡儂背囊<br />\n <br />\n雖然唔知背囊入面有乜，<span style=\"color: red;\">但係如果咁唔好彩銀包同身分證明文件，就等於拉咗一個手足<br />\n</span>，有埋證據可以落charge<br />\n<br />\n所以用79蚊背囊，或者背囊有胸扣，發夢都扣返好個扣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36c8a61a0b6aaf3d3ed5a61c9e5d1241d75a52f9","tid":1503120,"uid":42852,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T23:09:40.000Z","msg":"自推10連 1"},{"pid":"7577f3fcd801fcc078fdc46b7fc7d4630713043e","tid":1503120,"uid":42852,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T23:09:56.000Z","msg":"自推10連 2"},{"pid":"123a8eb5a9127162d12c223bd3ada35a150635e4","tid":1503120,"uid":42852,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T23:10:15.000Z","msg":"自推10連 3"},{"pid":"07b1181c04c2183b7ecafa2888d5a539fcef12a2","tid":1503120,"uid":42852,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T23:10:33.000Z","msg":"自推10連 4"},{"pid":"cfce3aca48a3a3fabbce19000eb555e52c8d4ad9","tid":1503120,"uid":42852,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T23:11:27.000Z","msg":"狗狗秒速負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1ab287d9034562d6e888229315ebbca6b129b69","tid":1503120,"uid":210328,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T23:11:55.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74